description: The smokiest truck in Miami serves a variety of slow smoked foods. Using only hardwoods & freshest ingredients. We even bake our own breads! Whatever you desire, we can create a menu for you! Want a smoked taco, quesadilla, burger? Just ask! From smoked pork, chicken, fish & sandwiches, we will satisfy your tummy! We can also create a kid friendly menu so let us know what you desire. we do it all!
name: Holy Smoked
